:274722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"夜晚我見到Facebook死黑警惹沙士<br />\n和同僚共享 宿舍班狗 都一一感染<br />\n黎病發喇 訓哂響醫院 之不過再冇得醫<br />\n邊一件未訓 我也有信心 最終都會咳死<br />\n<br />\n班Po Po感染 武漢沙士<br />\n升天不升柴 人人患病就令肺會花<br />\n<br />\n班Po Po感染 武漢沙士<br />\n打得多人原來現在比天收<br />\nHong Kong Police<br />\n<br />\n人人入貨 齊開香檳 死黑警惹沙士<br />\n寧願日日 黑警確診 兼死多d<br />\n就當報應 只因當初 晚晚放TG<br />\n點樣病發到致死 佢都只係抵死<br />\n<br />\n班Po Po感染 武漢沙士<br />\n升天不升柴 人人患病就令肺會花<br />\n<br />\n班Po Po感染 武漢沙士<br />\n打得多人原來現在比天收<br />\nHong Kong Police<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班Po Po感染 武漢沙士<br />\n升天不升柴 人人患病就令肺會花<br />\n班Po Po感染 武漢沙士<br />\n打得多人原來現在比天收<br />\nHong Kong Police"},{"pid":"4508b7e25233e0f4c578b061b5ede146375a5a93","tid":1942692,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227133b26b3702488dd2048b5c7e8112ceb47cdd","tid":1942692,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bbb20f57324bdb1cb05351243d3b6149f5ed0b65","tid":1942692,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"聽講好多雌犬同班師兄大sir成日gathering <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"係好撚多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c20133a7eece99898c790503e68ccb4c6e7871","tid":1942692,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,